reviewText: Bought this for my mother for Christmas. She's enjoying them very much. Highly recommend!
Actually no stars. These are not licenced material, not even professionally reproduced pirated material. Please stop selling this junk, garbage. Never has an amazon order upset me so much as this.
Wonderful.  My mother in-law from Cuba can't take her eyes off of the DVDs.

So far two videos show problems, it is not my video machine.. I have questions about this....the delivery was prompt but there are quite a few DVDs and I don't know if all have problems, I have not finished  viewing them. Please advise. Thanks.. Franchesca.
